            <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Avesta:</strong> The sacred scriptures of Zoroastrianism</li>
                <li><strong>Gathas:</strong> Hymns attributed to Zarathustra himself, the oldest part of the Avesta</li>
                <li><strong>Yasna:</strong> Liturgical texts including the Gathas, used in worship ceremonies</li>
                <li><strong>Bundahishn:</strong> "Creation" - Zoroastrian cosmology and cosmogony</li>
                <li><strong>Denkard:</strong> Encyclopedia of Zoroastrian beliefs and customs</li>
